## What It Does NOT Do

- ❌ Does **not** perform audio analysis (uses P1-A1 + P1-A2)
- ❌ Does **not** generate DMX from scratch (requires DMXEngine)
- ❌ Does **not** provide fixture profiles (uses P2-D1)
- ❌ Does **not** handle show control (use P2-D4 for cues)
- ❌ Does **not** do advanced lighting design (use external software)
- ❌ Does **not** store audio-reactive presets (use StateManager)

