## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Audio latency affecting sync | Medium | High | Optimize audio pipeline, buffer management |
| DMX value jumps causing light flicker | Medium | Medium | Smoothing, rate limiting |
| High CPU with many fixtures | Medium | High | Frame skipping, LOD (level of detail) |
| Fixture compatibility issues | Medium | Medium | Fixture profiles, capability detection |
| Thread contention | Low | Medium | Lock-free design, atomic updates |

